      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "runSalesAgent(sellerId)\nsweeps every owned listing -> calls the SAME ensureAgent() / tick()\nthe Listing Agent uses -- skips agent-lock.ts-locked listings\n+ one Sales-Agent-only lever: relist\n(un-escalate a donated/recycled listing if geo-demand improves past 1.15x margin)",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "sa1",
      "originalText": "runSalesAgent(sellerId)\nsweeps every owned listing -> calls the SAME ensureAgent() / tick()\nthe Listing Agent uses -- skips agent-lock.ts-locked listings\n+ one Sales-Agent-only lever: relist\n(un-escalate a donated/recycled listing if geo-demand improves past 1.15x margin)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 13
